name: MXSignpostIntervalData
desc: A data object representing the captured data for a custom metric.

items.name: var histogrammedSignpostDuration: MXHistogram<UnitDuration>
items.desc: A histogram of the different time intervals of a custom metric event.

items.name: var averageMemory: MXAverage<UnitInformationStorage>?
items.desc: The average memory used during the logged intervals.

items.name: var cumulativeCPUTime: Measurement<UnitDuration>?
items.desc: The total amount of CPU time used during the logged intervals.

items.name: var cumulativeLogicalWrites: Measurement<UnitInformationStorage>?
items.desc: The total amount of data written to disk or other long term storage during the logged intervals.

items.name: var cumulativeHitchTimeRatio: Measurement<Unit>?
items.desc: The ratio of the total time spent hitching to the total time spent animating during the logged intervals.
